text: Elze's Life () is a 2000 Lithuanian German drama movie directed by Algimantas Puipa and starring Eglė Jaselskytė, Kostas Smoriginas, Janina Lapinskaitė, Andrius Paulavičius. == Other websites == * Category:2000 drama movies Category:Lithuanian movies Category:German drama movies Category:Movies directed by Algimantas Puipa
